text:
I am giving a talk at Cambridge University tomorrow as part of their Research Software Engineering seminar series. It will give an overview of the work of the R Contribution Working Group (and my role in it, as part of my RSE fellowship), which will be old news to some folks here, but if you are relatively new to this Slack and the activities of the RCWG you might like to join the Zoom!

Thursday 2 November, 13:00-14:00 UTC
